Using Beyond Compare 4:

1. Open to compare both files ("usb_xxx-original.x" on left and "usb_xxx-patched.x" on right)
2. Session -> Text Compare Report
	Report Layout: Patch
	Report Options: Normal Diff
	Output Options: Plain text
	Click "Copy to Clipboard"
3. Paste DIFF to "patches\usb_xxx.patch" file